data.description: Fabulous home in quiet cove! Ranch style 3 BR/2 BA split plan with an abundance of natural light and beautiful hardwood flooring in all living areas and new carpet in the bedrooms! Stylishly painted and updated with gorgeous woodwork! Super open plan features XL Great Room and Dining Room with windows overlooking private backyard! Freshly painted inside & low maint vinyl exterior! NEWHeat and Air in 2022! Wood-fenced back yard & cozy courtyard at front of home! Award winning Bartlett schools!
